// This file contains variables for different themes

export const light = {
    body: "fff",
    text: "#202020",
    bodyRgba: "255, 255, 255",
    textRgba: "32, 32, 32",

    carouselColor: '#EEEDDE',
    logoColor: '#FF6410',

    fontxs: '0.75em',
    fontsm: '0.875em',
    fontmd: '1em',
    fontlg: '1.25e,',
    fontxl: '2em',
    fontxxl: '3em',
    fontxxxl: '4em',

    fontButton: '4em',

    navHeight: '5rem',
}

export const dark = {
    body: "#808080",
    text: "#202020",
    bodyRgba: "255, 255, 255",
    textRgba: "32, 32, 32",

    carouselColor: '#EEEDDE',

    fontxs: '0.75em',
    fontsm: '0.875em',
    fontmd: '1em',
    fontlg: '1.25e,',
    fontxl: '2em',
    fontxxl: '3em',
    fontxxxl: '4em',

    fontButton: '4em',

    navHeight: '5rem',
}
